title: Best of The Program | Guest: Justin Haskins | 11/4/21
description:
President Biden and the Democrats have failed to learn after Election Day 2021’s red wave. Biden’s vaccine mandate is around the corner, so Glenn and Stu review it and the power it will give OSHA. “The Great Reset” co-author Justin Haskins joins to break down Biden’s new partnership with the World Economic Forum.
